{"legislative_session": "2026", "identifier": "SB2258", "title": "RELATING TO LOCAL PURCHASING PREFERENCE.", "from_organization": "~{\"classification\": \"upper\"}", "classification": ["bill"], "subject": ["Compost", "DAGS", "DCR", "DOD", "DOE", "DOH", "Landscaping Materials", "Local Preference", "Mulch", "Reports", "Soil", "UH"], "abstracts": [{"note": "description", "abstract": "Gradually requires that, by 2032, 30% of the natural landscaping materials purchased by certain departments be locally sourced, meaning 50% of the wholesale value is added by manufacture, processing, production, or harvesting in the State.  Applies to the Department of Education, Department of Health, Department of Corrections and Rehabilitation, Department of Defense, Department of Accounting and General Services, and University of Hawaii System.  Requires annual reports to the Legislature.  Effective 1/1/2525.  (SD1)"}], "other_titles": [], "other_identifiers": [{"identifier": "ocd-bill-hi-2026-sb2258"}], "actions": [{"description": "Report adopted; Passed Second Reading, as amended (SD 1) and referred to WAM.", "date": "2026-02-19", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"upper\"}", "classification": ["passage", "reading-2", "referral-committee"], "related_entities": [{"name": "Ways and Means", "entity_type": "organization", "organization_id": null}]}, {"description": "Reported from GVO/CPN (Stand. Com. Rep. No. 2473) with recommendation of passage on Second Reading, as amended (SD 1) and referral to WAM.", "date": "2026-02-19", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"upper\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "The committee(s) on  CPN recommend(s) that the measure be PASSED, WITH AMENDMENTS.  The votes in CPN were as follows: 4 Aye(s): Senator(s) Keohokalole, Fukunaga, McKelvey, Awa; Aye(s) with reservations: none ; 0 No(es): none; and 1 Excused: Senator(s) Lamosao.", "date": "2026-02-11", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"upper\"}", "cl